default              defaultMr Timpson:default I have two views about champions. One is that there is always merit in looking at having a leader of a profession, an issue or a particular vulnerable group, such as victims. My second view is that it is only worth doing if, first, you can find the right person with the qualities to make a difference in that role, and also if the role has teeth attached to it. 
default              
